title: Reproduce FIM Evaluation
body: Hello, thanks a lot for your great work. Could you kindly advise on how to reproduce the evaluation results of FIM as shown in Table 6 of your [paper](https://arxiv.org/abs/2401.14196)? I tried to use [bigcode-evaluation](https://github.com/bigcode-project/bigcode-evaluation-harness) on `Santacoder_FIM` with the [Insertion prompt](https://github.com/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-Coder#2-code-insertion) structure from this repository, but it still generates very long content and I can't reproduce the results in the paper.
author: Hambaobao
